title: Saints, 'Jacks Get NCHA Preseason Report Card
text:
Saints, 'Jacks Get NCHA Preseason Report Card 
By Zach Schneider Saints, 'Jacks Get NCHA Preseason Report Card   5:48 PM CDT 
Duluth, MN (NNCNOW.com) --- The St. Scholastica men's hockey team has been picked fifth and Northland has been picked ninth in the Northern Collegiate Hockey Association (NCHA) preseason coaches' poll, which was released on Wednesday afternoon. 
Adrian is again the league favorite after having won the regular season title in six of the past seven seasons, receiving nine of a possible 10 first-place votes.
